* &quot;Hearts and Minds&quot; (&quot;Lost&quot;)
* &quot;Hearts and Minds&quot; (&quot;The Outer Limits&quot;)
* &quot;Hearts and Minds&quot; (&quot;That&#x27;s So Raven&quot;)

