<doc id="1045074" wikidata="Q113954014" url="?curid=1045074" title="Place of refuge">
<text>A place of refuge includes various places where people can seek refuge:

* An asylum (antiquity), in antiquity, a place (usually a temple) where people could seek refuge
* A sovereign offering the right of asylum
* A sanctuary, a place offering safety from persecution
* Place of refuge for ships, for ships in distress</text><links>
